IOGate - Class in net.entersol.iogate
This class gives a standard gate to the GWT to communicate with the server it uses built in classes to communicate over HTTP(S) and wraps them with nicer interface.
IOGate() - Constructor for class net.entersol.iogate.IOGate
This is default constructor that uses default server "localhost" to connect with and sets privacyLevel as public
IOGate(String) - Constructor for class net.entersol.iogate.IOGate
This constructor uses the given server to connect with
IOGate(String, String) - Constructor for class net.entersol.iogate.IOGate
This constructor uses default server "localhost" and privacyLevel is private
IOGate(String, String, String) - Constructor for class net.entersol.iogate.IOGate
This constructor uses private privacyLevel and sets the server that should connect to
IOGateException - Exception in net.entersol.iogate
This exception class contains information about the failure of the connection that has been established between client and server
IOGateException() - Constructor for exception net.entersol.iogate.IOGateException
Default constructor
IOGateException(String) - Constructor for exception net.entersol.iogate.IOGateException
This constructor sets the message for the exception
IOGateException(String, int, String) - Constructor for exception net.entersol.iogate.IOGateException
This constructor allows to specify message, status code of the server and status text
IOResponce - Interface in net.entersol.iogate
Server response will goes to one of these functions if IOGate class is used to communicate with server then this interface should be implemented and an instant of it passes to the calling function.
IOService - Class in net.entersol.iogate
This class creates an abstraction layer upon IOGate connection this class aims specific to the services not to the server.
IOService() - Constructor for class net.entersol.iogate.IOService
Default constructor; this constructor creates a connection to the default server (localhost) without any service selected
IOService(IOGate) - Constructor for class net.entersol.iogate.IOService
This constructor connects to the gate that provided but without selecting any service.
IOService(IOGate, String, String, String) - Constructor for class net.entersol.iogate.IOService
This constructor connects to the given gate and selects the service
